photography, creative portfolio, and blog site.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/gallerix-creative-gallery-portfolio-and-blog-theme/20725461\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Amy Gallerix</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Smart</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Smart is a multi-purpose theme suitable for any type of publisher.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/smart-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/17333318\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Smart</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Royal</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Royal is a clean and modern one page WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/royal-responsive-one-page-parallax-wordpress-theme/19560027\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Royal</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ambra</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Minimal Marketplace WordPress Theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/ambra-minimal-marketplace-wordpress-theme/20169380\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Ambra</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6n