2017/11/wpmlacstraduction-300x176.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlacstraduction-150x88.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlacstraduction.png 371w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ACSTraduction is an innovative and forward-thinking translation agency specializing in legal, technical, and communications (web and marketing) sectors.</p>\n<p>As language service experts in more than 20 languages, ACSTraduction can handle all your translation and interpreting needs. With seven in-house translators on-staff as well as many specialized translators on-call, ACSTraduction strives to bring personalized customer service and high-quality translations.</p>\n<p>ACSTraduction‚Äôs website translation service includes translations for websites, web applications, tablets and smartphones, software, e-newsletters, and e-mails.</p>\n<p>With ACSTraduction you will receive:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Personalized follow-up on every project</li>\n<li>Meticulous quality assurance</li>\n<li>Data confidentiality</li>\n<li>Prompt responsiveness (i.e., within an hour!)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1424853\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1-300x33.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"664\" height=\"73\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1-300x33.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1-150x16.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1-768x83.png 768w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1-1024x111.png 1024w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/acsmethod-1.png 1509w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 664px) 100vw, 664px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you are already a WPML user and interested in using ACSTraduction for translation, follow the instructions for<a href=\"https://wpml.org/translation-service/acstraduction/\"> translating WordPress sites with ACSTraduction</a>. If you are new to WPML, feel free to purchase the <a href=\"https://wpml.org/purchase/\">Multilingual CMS</a> package and get started.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=jHrM20Q6QZE:dEo89L-qBLw:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=jHrM20Q6QZE:dEo89L-qBLw:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=jHrM20Q6QZE:dEo89L-qBLw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=jHrM20Q6QZE:dEo89L-qBLw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=jHrM20Q6QZE:dEo89L-qBLw:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=jHrM20Q6QZE:dEo89L-qBLw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/jHrM20Q6QZE\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://wpml.org/2017/11/wpml-welcomes-acstraduction-as-a-new-translation-partner/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://wpml.org/2017/11/wpml-welcomes-acstraduction-as-a-new-translation-partner/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s: