\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5585:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-975307\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png\" alt=\"WPML Compatible themes\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several WPML compatible themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are: <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/lynk-social-networking-and-community-wordpress-theme/20287264\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Lynk</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/seese-responsive-ecommerce-theme/19551597\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Seese</a>, <a href=\"https://www.pixelemu.com/wordpress-themes/i/3-business/237-business\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">PE Business</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/vitrine-woocommerce-wordpress-theme/19951364\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vitrine</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/ed-school-elementary-middle-and-highschool-wordpress-theme/19618075\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Ed School</a>, <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/desire-sexy-shop/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Desire Sexy Shop</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you‚Äôre a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it c